
===================================
📌 1. Finglish Version (Persian Latin Script)
===================================

📖 **Tashrih:**
    Dastoor `deb-reversion` baraye bargardandan version-e package `.deb` be version-e ghabli estefade mishavad. In be shoma komak mikonad agar update jadid moshkel dashte bashad.

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    🔹 `deb-reversion package_name [version]`  --> 📦 Package-e morede nazar va version-e bargashti ra moshakhas mikonad. Agar version ra nazanid, akharin version-e ghabli ra bargardand.
    🔹 `-h`, `--help` --> ❓ Rahnamaye dastoor ra neshon midahad.
    🔹 `-n`, `--no-remove` --> 🚫 Package-e jadid ra hazf nemikonad, fagat downgrade mikonad. (Ehtiat: momken ast problem be vojood biarad)

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**

    $ sudo deb-reversion firefox

    🔹 Bargardandan Firefox be akharin version-e ghabli.

    $ sudo deb-reversion chromium 83.0.4103.61-0ubuntu0.20.04.1

    🔹 Bargardandan Chromium be version-e moshakhas shode.

✅ **Mesal sade:**

    $ sudo deb-reversion vlc

